      </div>

      <div class="flex items-end gap-3 justify-end ml-auto max-w-[80%]">
        <div class="space-y-1 text-right">
          <div class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-[2rem] rounded-br-none shadow-md">
            <p class="text-sm font-medium">Haha that's so sweet! My boy Buster is the same way with Labradors. He's very energetic! 🎾</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant/50 mr-2">10:20 AM</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-end gap-3 max-w-[80%]">
        <img class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full object-cover shadow-sm" alt="Puppy profile avatar" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD1z5H3XlMEBBsPCdcSql-uPKfToWN2ai4xbEJUtGQ44JNy8mTsO3LB5T408YJE74xs1ZND74gIj_vYwiciOp5Nxnq_J4r5k9TToOAtxDXj5chmAds5aJjXy6q8jc5zha2An7MCQY4n8KK9Lg2_QgehXSb65Z4Lo0Cbcf_Tq8P2H_E9OUxQtKUrrKX8vGGzm0SG9wbC7yHLApVhDPxZL8kzRHnscGaf9fz5TEiy_6oNrESsuP5kQXWb-0FS6AbAy4MU9yJI2Rgpoj0"/>
        <div class="space-y-1">
