            <p class="text-sm font-medium">Cooper is 2 years old and loves a good chase! We usually go to Central Bark on weekends. Is he free for a playdate? 🐶✨</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 max-w-sm">
            <img class="rounded-2xl object-cover h-36 w-full shadow-sm hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform" alt="Two happy dogs playing together" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBUypp3CuAahCvuz1Hi3eivtG3Pslcn5iLz0-7iMogLQ2i7lJXXxlmWsKS1gUAtJZisJlgZBwonfwjrOazhe5s6qLx1mL8OuBrqYgNEx3jtlumBtHytCyQ1WlJTKSnk8rwvuHyv5Y5J3ar3vID9NZlyopFAqfsS7U8xc1KK6KTn8cOj_ViS9picz4keiQx0jq16r-VTzmO25f6u4CFshdzOXbR0aSxeZ6uQtOtVvnA-8ZiNoiPPj1fKq7wbng2VcBZ_vq-IxBVFFRc"/>
            <img class="rounded-2xl object-cover h-36 w-full shadow-sm hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform" alt="Dog jumping to catch a ball" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCpzgNqxb0EvA3WL_NU9yaOkl1z9irn2cERbOyYJ0u4K0QPi98sSTYdY6corL1SgPwVJqY7jM5g55c1A0NipP_7FrDm3V7xVxGXexqWCm8cltbZx8lEuIsFLEVF3ZhX2r0o1AC3CLM-FVfWu_VG4l-HshG_YgvdV49Lk6wYWBJTltUAdyddv8WsqoUWEMfSEUXAF8k09xUqKxIzU1AE1kpOcKnuI-DmP3kJla8GDQEskr89wNV7Uz5zibJIaO6xkM-aRFLCIqL34NA"/>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant/50 ml-2">10:42 AM</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="p-6 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-md">
